caption.title: Phylogenetic analysis of the CprM gene sequences of DENV-3 isolates from the Klang Valley.
caption.p: Sample sequences of DENV-3 (240 nt) from Ae. aegypti (indicated with an asterisk *) and Ae. albopictus collected from Selangor (indicated with a white triangle) and Kuala Lumpur (indicated with a black triangle) in this study are labelled with the GenBank accession number, sample ID and year of collection. Bootstrap values (1,000 replicates) are shown next to the branches. Taxa of reference sequences are labelled as the GenBank accession numbers, year and country of sample collection.
